{"tid":226772,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[求分享] To defer or not to defer","createTime":"2017-05-02T17:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T10:47:57.000Z","uid":84298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe2eb6113b54fd4d8a742890e8036b38682d93c7","tid":226772,"uid":84298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:26:28.000Z","msg":"雖然爆肝去chur credit可以準時畢業<br />\n但唔想又辛苦又爛GPA<br />\n呢家考慮緊de唔defer<br />\n<br />\n一來將D科分散去讀，可以Keep到個GPA（想報Master）<br />\n二來大學資源太多，想用盡多一年（報Prog etc）<br />\n而defer個年打算考埋車牌，同埋Yr4 summer可以搵好intern<br />\n<br />\n不過我好摺，唔鐘意住hall、上莊<br />\n所以呢家諗緊有咩想做<br />\n等自己可以係踏出社會前多一年，做想做GE野，先再出黎做野<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲係過來人比D經驗／意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7133ac263eea25f261f4fa21a4d47084f3f41dad","tid":226772,"uid":101467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:36:28.000Z","msg":"如果你想充實啲就de啦 嚟緊幾廿年有排你翻工啦 真係咁趕咩 同埋出到嚟好多野想做都唔會做到架喇<br />\n<br />\n利申 yr3 準備de"},{"pid":"99728a903914be619bd725dce56dd43ee2696f6e","tid":226772,"uid":84298,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f422f2d3ffbe8ea5f29953ef47c8846b7ee20d08","tid":226772,"uid":84298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1442b1f97bb9b0704d31f89e66529f9194a5c830","tid":226772,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:11:15.000Z","msg":"not"},{"pid":"c8e511ecf81bb96cf5d3713d7515b538d08370a2","tid":226772,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:16:15.00